OL,4,CUber to pay drivers a minimum wage,
OL,5,Choliday pay and pensions
OL,6, Uber says it will give its UK drivers a
OL,7, guaranteed minimum wage, holiday pay
OL,8, and pensions.
OL,10,FThe ride-hailing app giant said drivers
OL,11,Fwould earn at least the UK's National
OL,12,FLiving Wage, paid to the over 25s, of
OL,13,F#8.72 an hour.
OL,15,FIt comes one month after the US firm
OL,16,Flost a legal battle in the UK, begun in
OL,17,F2016, over drivers' status.
OL,19,FUber told the BBC it did not expect the
OL,20,Fchange in drivers' conditions to mean
OL,21,Fhigher fares.
